        <Parent_String>designers [300025190], people in the visual arts [300025101], people in the visual arts and related occupations [300239109], people in the arts [300168455], people in the arts and related occupations [300168331], people in the humanities [300025485], people by occupation [300024980], people (agents) [300024979], People (hierarchy name) [300024978], Agents Facet [300264089]</Parent_String>
