    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Designers of all visual aspects of a stage production, including scenery, properties, lighting, costume, and makeup. For artists who paint theatrical scenery, prefer "theatrical painters." For those who design the visual aspects of a film or television production, use "production designers."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079228/Grove Art Online (2008-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>In de meest algemene zin verwijst deze term naar ontwerpers van alle visuele aspecten van een toneelproductie, met inbegrip van het decor, de rekwisieten, de belichting, de kostuums en de make-up. Vroeger verwees de term ook naar decorschilders, kunstenaars die toneeldecors schilderden.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052403/Van Dale Groot Woordenboek (1998)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>廣義而言，可泛指負責舞台作品所有視覺元素的設計師，包括佈景、道具、燈光、服裝及化妝。此詞彙原先指負責繪製劇場佈景的美術創作家。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
